er der Polemik. Einige Beiträge widmen sich Karl Kraus und der komplexen Beziehung, die Musil mit diesem verband. Ein umfangreicher Rezensionsteil befasst sich mit neuen Publikationen zu Musil und zur Literatur der klassischen Moderne.  aThe Musil-Forum, the publication series of the International Robert Musil Society, is an interdisciplinary platform for research into the literature of classical modernism and, in particular, the works of Robert Musil (1880–1942).  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Okt 2021) 4aKraus, Karl. 4aMusil, Robert. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh  aDöblin, Alfred.  aMusil, Robert.1 aArburg, Hans-Georg von, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBanki, Luisa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBertschik, Julia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDröscher-Teille, Mandy, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGerigk, Anja, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGschwandtner, Harald, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGumbrecht, Hans Ulrich, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHoffmann, Birthe, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHonold, Alexander, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aInnerhofer, Roland, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKappeler, Florian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKaufmann, Kira, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKrause, Robert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKucher, Primus Heinz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 